function Global_updateCookie() {
    var zip = $('#txtNewZipCodeCookie').val();
    if (zip != '' && zip.length == 5 && isNaN(zip) == false ) {
        setCookie('ZipCodeCookie1', zip);
        $('#divError').hide();
    } else {
        $('#divError').show();
    }
}

                        return false;

                            return false;

                            jqButton.first().click();

function Global_checkForCookie(url) {
    if (Global_getZipCodeCookie("ZipCodeCookie1") != null) {
        document.location = url;
    } else {
        $('#dvNewZipCodeCookie').dialog('open');
        $('#btnNewZipCodeCookie').attr('onclick', 'Global_updateCookie(); Global_checkForCookie("' + url + '");');
    }
}

function Global_getZipCodeCookie(name) {
    return $.cookie(name);
